# Faz 5: Admin & Analytics Panel — Detayli Implementation Plani

## Genel Mimari Kararlar
- `IDbContextFactory<AppDbContext>` — her component kendi DbContext'ini acar, hemen dispose eder
- **AdminDataService** singleton — tum DB sorgu logic buraya, component'larda raw DbContext YOK
- **ConfigService** singleton — in-memory runtime parametreler
- **LiveFeedService YOK** — Admin salt okunur analitik, Worker calismak zorunda degil
- **Auto-migrate on startup** — Dashboard ile ayni pattern
- **Port 5002** — launchSettings.json
- **ApexCharts** — tum chartlar icin (LightweightCharts KULLANMA)
- Tailwind dark theme — Dashboard ile birebir ayni CSS degiskenleri, sadece accent rengi **purple** (`#a855f7`)

